Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.70,0:00:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯，這次你又幹了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.11,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
