Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.72,0:01:34.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.07,0:01:48.38,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.45,0:01:57.62,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}起手有回真小人\NTakeback
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.59,0:03:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼心事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只慘遭基爾特公會襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.86,0:03:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士又說要留在銀之戰艦上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.23,0:03:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心發生紅視現象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，我以前也曾經碰到過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.77,0:03:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在失去知覺之前\N那感覺好難形容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.58,0:03:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問您要點什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.48,0:03:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我一杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時價？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.42,0:03:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這頂級水是取自即使在這裡\N也很難入手的水源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.49,0:03:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天只要80克勞地亞而已哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,80克勞地亞！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.87,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次你們又大幹了一場是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是這次需要補充的彈藥\N以及補給品的清單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.44,0:04:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請優先更換升降機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕著要出發\N裝甲和砲台的修理也請儘快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.05,0:04:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就萬事拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長妳要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.03,0:04:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是頂級水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.94,0:04:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在這種地方再碰到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.08,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…你是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？妳不記得了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.19,0:04:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我的水壺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…什麼來著？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.84,0:04:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍，莫藍‧謝蘭度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…換句話說你是被炒魷魚了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，是我主動辭職的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是因為我們的關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你們沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外頭不是停著一艘\N叫做格拉艾斯號的貴族艦嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很氣派的那艘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去那艘船上工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.93,0:05:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也有推薦信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.50,0:05:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要有這些生還章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是穩操勝算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穩操什麼勝算啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在跑了 在跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到這兒來怎麼可以不玩這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，借過一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.00,0:05:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，這兒貴族還真多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外頭停著那艘號稱\N毫髮無傷的帝王格拉艾斯號喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說落跑王格拉艾斯號嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓，你說得太大聲了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，可不可以讓個位子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天這裡已經被我們包下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.05,0:06:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你們周圍\N你們不覺得你們身分不對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭博和階級哪有什麼相關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.13,0:06:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.26,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個傭兵還想怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道格拉艾斯號\N是直屬於皇帝陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還敢這樣撒野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.64,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要那麼衝動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.74,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們才剛到而已\N總之先去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝完了再賭一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.75,0:06:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等玩夠了再來扯這個也不遲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少爺，來一杯那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.86,0:06:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，馬上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.83,0:07:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.94,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想到那種人的船上去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.54,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作輕鬆錢又多，不是很好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且最棒的一點是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在格拉艾斯號上\N就絕對死不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好差哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.17,0:07:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳可以下去到船塢散散心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，我們一起去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，我想去睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶，贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我們的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天運氣不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.66,0:08:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，沒鬧事果然是正確的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正確，正確，太正確了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的比賽\N由於跑道上有障礙物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.57,0:08:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣告無效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,障礙物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.74,0:08:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莊家就和基爾特公會一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說的話就是規則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.41,0:08:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想參加賭局\N就要服從他的判決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承您抬舉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.42,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑道上是有障礙物沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.46,0:08:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就忍耐一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好，一次就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.99,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不服我的話\N就請你們退場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得下不為例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那隻紅的看起來跑得很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看牠還在兇別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.58,0:09:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭紅色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要選那隻白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.79,0:09:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，牠動也不動\N正在養精蓄銳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.22,0:09:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看只是在打瞌睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種類型\N在緊要關頭才會使出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我賭這隻瞌睡蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照現在的賭盤來看\N妳是沒有贏的希望啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.43,0:09:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊，瞌睡蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.87,0:09:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不比比看怎麼知道誰贏誰輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是開先鋒艇的是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那東西感覺怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是問妳飛起來感覺怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.12,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上在一大片天空裡\N好像只剩下我們自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是指妳和那小子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為一個人沒辦法飛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛翔在天空感覺一定很棒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.89,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.13,0:10:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，這是今晚最後一場比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.00,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精彩可期哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色火花今晚只要贏了\N就是五連霸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強勢的紅蛇\N應該也會有亮麗的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雞王和綠色颱風也不可忽視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，看仔細了下仔細了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要選紅色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.58,0:10:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唉，不在工作崗位的時候\N就不要選紅色的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色那隻果然沒什麼人氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人氣算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.45,0:10:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡蟲，讓大家對你刮目相看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.20,0:10:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格拉艾斯號的艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.77,0:11:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一副討人厭的長相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色火花應該不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.32,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是金色好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點，最後一場要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也快來呀，不要趕不上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？艾麗絲蒂亞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問妳有沒有看到拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後面的往裡面擠一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的傷口不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.81,0:11:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.08,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.16,0:12:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全看你的囉，紅色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.90,0:12:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛全部的人都要賭同一隻啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡蟲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.30,0:12:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色的快跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.11,0:12:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超過牠們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.14,0:12:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好，不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是艦長\N看來又要刷新連勝記錄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.15,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡蟲，你在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.75,0:12:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.73,0:12:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？莫藍呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,金色那隻好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穩贏的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是艦長，眼光真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.51,0:12:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想為\N像您這樣的艦長效勞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位實在太幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪條船上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過去曾在\N旗艦克勞索拉斯號上服務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.69,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，他非常的了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.53,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也多虧了司令的栽培\N才能有今天的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上我還有他的推薦信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.41,0:13:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來他還活著啊\N那個鄉下貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您看那個人的胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.51,0:13:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在戰場出生入死的證明\N正是我的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米納紀斯會被度西斯佔領
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是因為\N麥德賽在作戰中逃跑的緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.02,0:13:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在那種膽小鬼的船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意當然是要多少有多少囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就是卑鄙小人的證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.50,0:13:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種卑賤的東西\N你還真好意思拿出來給人看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色那隻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.85,0:14:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰才是卑鄙小人哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這東西對你很重要不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.36,0:14:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來，要好好拿著才行哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還差一個\N我就可以出人頭地了說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.26,0:14:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍，你不管到哪裡\N都可以混得很好的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色那隻好厲害\N居然追上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦，打起精神來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看連那隻瞌睡蟲\N都在努力奮戰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊，瞌睡蟲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.05,0:14:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊，衝啊衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下不削翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.02,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.06,0:14:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死也不能輸呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.56,0:14:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜，你的自尊到哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.57,0:14:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太不夠狠了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒！拿酒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞌睡蟲，只剩那隻金色的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下可有看頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有驚無險哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.57,0:15:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡，艦長您選的金色\N怎麼可能輸給那些下等的鳥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是這麼認為呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是作弊嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.63,0:15:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弱女子遭人欺負囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.30,0:16:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可以不去挺身搭救呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.84,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總不成眼睜睜在一旁看著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.14,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.44,0:16:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在找尤莉絲嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.11,0:16:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上聽說\N有和EXILE相關的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會出現在最近的黑市拍賣上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是圖嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.72,0:16:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表面上這是一場\N獎金很高的先鋒艇競賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.39,0:16:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實背後同時也在進行著\N黑市交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚還挺熱鬧的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是那些有錢的白癡貴族們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.04,0:16:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群凱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇妳搞過頭了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.52,0:16:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.25,0:16:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大騙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.06,0:16:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.03,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在米納紀斯連打都沒打就逃的\N根本就只有你那艘格拉艾斯號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.98,0:17:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.55,0:17:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.22,0:17:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是一個小小的槍兵\N居然敢侮辱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這可是叛逆皇帝的重罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格拉艾斯號上\N全都是一群卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是不想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我渥克的船塢裡\N不准有人隨便亂來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.86,0:18:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這種像垃圾一樣的槍兵侮辱\N教我怎麼忍得下這口氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侮辱人的應該是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲結束了，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.27,0:18:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你連一句道歉都沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情大條了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.58,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.69,0:18:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要髒了您的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.79,0:18:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是用軍艦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用軍艦決鬥\N看我把你連人帶船一起擊沈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.67,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來當見證人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體上船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.57,0:18:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.60,0:18:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就一起去跟閻王爺報到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那群野蠻的猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要讓他們知道我的厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，那不會是銀之戰艦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說那傢伙不就是\N亞力克斯‧羅威了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是殺無赦的銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.01,0:19:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是無敵戰艦…我們完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被幹掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦，有沒有什麼對策啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在開砲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.09,0:19:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果從背後攻擊\N就算是銀之戰艦也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.79,0:19:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是還沒有發信號耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要贏了\N事後理由大可以隨便編
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要發射嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主砲，射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好機會，射啊，射啊射啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要停給我射個痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，本艦大獲全勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.16,0:20:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的銀之戰艦\N知道我的厲害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.03,0:20:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼那麼慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試試看那個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.94,0:20:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.97,0:20:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下可以跟令尊\N大大誇耀一番了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是\N父親大人一定會很開心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要確實作好記錄的收集工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備發射多管噴射穿甲彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.65,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下你們完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.86,0:20:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無敵戰艦的稱號\N這下要讓給我們格拉艾斯號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定信號彈已發出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.27,0:21:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.62,0:21:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞得那麼誇張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發出信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確定決鬥結束，銀之戰艦獲勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.50,0:21:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會本著見證人的責任\N向國家進行報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.64,0:21:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追加…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也請替收拾善後的人想想好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是航行順利結束\N再一起好好喝一杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.11,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渥克 上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.15,0:21:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直太慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.93,0:22:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生還章給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好你沒坐上那艘船
